cs.SI, cs.SOC, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR 

This paper focuses on modeling social influence in predicting event attendance using social network data. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper also uses graph embedding techniques and a neural network for classification, which suggests possible categories of cs.SOC (Social and Information Networks), cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
